long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Workspace Chrome Extension By ThirdEye for Conference Calls. Use this chrome extension to schedule conference calls. Follow below Steps
1. Install the Extension
2. Go to Google Calendar 
3. Click on Add a ThirdEye Workspace Meeting  Button.
